description:
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an experienced nurse manager with a proven track record of leadership and change management to be part of our senior team.This is an exciting opportunity to lead the site team in the operational day to day flow of patients through the emergency and elective pathway, ensuring safety and capacity is utilised appropriately.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will work with both internal and external stakeholders in ensuring the Trust can respond in line with local and national drivers, underpinned with policies, procedures and training.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you like the buzz of operational management, have excellent communication skills, have the desire to constantly strive in improving performance and an ability to work across system partners this may be the role for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Chinyama OkunugaManaging Director for Unplanned Care&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address : chinyama.okunuga@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number : 01438 314333&lt;/p&gt;
